# 🔎 Optional (very useful in OCP)

### 1. Actual usage (not just requests/limits)

```bash id="oc-top"
oc adm top pods -n your-namespace
```

---

### 2. Include persistent volume details

```bash id="pv-details"
oc get pv | grep your-namespace
```

---

### 3. Check quotas (important in OpenShift)

```bash id="quota"
oc get resourcequota -n your-namespace
```

